title: Volleycats start new streak
text: Tweet Joel Priest/Pine River Times Alex Forsythe has stepped in for the Ignacio Bobcats this year, and her serving along with the strong serving of Shoshone Thompson helped the Bobcats win a second consecutive game this week. The Bobcats beat Mancos 25-6, 25-12, 25-19.
